 timescales in the central region\nwould quickly lead to the formation of a nuclear star cluster.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 15 Feb 2019 19:00:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 23 Apr 2019 18:02:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-12"}
